channel.title: I got problem by putting my Rsps Public
channel.description: Ive tried all guides to put my rsps online but none will work for me, sometimes i test serverstatuschecker and that says my server is online but if i ask a friend to join, he cant connect to my server. I tried all ways to fix it but in none of guides i saw what to change in client.java or Server.java or other files to get it public. If someone wanna helps me i will realy really appreciate it and you will get staff rank if you play my server =) Greetz me =)
